queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `numrows` FROM ( SELECT `users`.*, IF(uid IS NULL, NULL, GROUP_CONCAT( JSON_OBJECT( 'faculty', `faculties`.`name`, 'department', `departments`.`name`, 'level', `levels`.`name`, 'form', `edForms`.`name`, 'code', `specialities`.`code`, 'speciality', `specialities`.`name`, 'course', `students`.`course`, 'group', students.grp ) ) ) AS list FROM `users` LEFT JOIN `students` ON `students`.`uid` = `users`.`id` LEFT JOIN `faculties` ON `faculties`.`id` = `students`.`faculty` LEFT JOIN `departments` ON `departments`.`id` = `students`.`department` LEFT JOIN `levels` ON `levels`.`id` = `students`.`level` LEFT JOIN `specialities` ON `specialities`.`id` = `students`.`speciality` LEFT JOIN `edForms` ON `edForms`.`id` = `students`.`form` WHERE `users`.`surname` LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' OR `users`.`name` LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' OR `users`.`patronymic` LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' OR `users`.`email` LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' OR CONCAT(users.surname, ' ', users.name, ' ', users.patronymic) LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' OR CONCAT(users.name, ' ', users.patronymic, ' ', users.surname) LIKE '%Александр%' ESCAPE '!' GROUP BY `users`.`id` ) CI_count_all_results
